title: I'll Name This Podcast Later Episode 93
description: Joe, Mal, & Rory sit down with Genius's Rob Markman and Hot 97's Scottie Beam to discuss the top 10 R&B artists of 2016 based upon vocals, singles, album, album sales/streams, impact, and touring; along with some other banter.
